> ## Background

**Gifte** is a florist in Medan, North Sumatra. Who weave stories through the language of flowers. They believe that every blossom holds a tale, and it's their dedication to bring each of their customer personal style and preferences to life through their exquisite creations that sets them apart. Working along with Jason Fonseca from [**Circles**](https://www.circlescreative.co) we create an attractive microsite to help Gifte's customer to experience a more dynamic and playful catalog that represent Gifte products in the offline event.

> ## My Work

- Create a mobile-first microsite that highlight the offline event theme products
- Implement several animations using framer-motion
- Create a door mask animation that will change dynamically.
